    <h1>Privacy Policy – Resonance Guitar Tuner</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 7, 2026</em></p>

    <p>Resonance Guitar Tuner ("the App") is a free tool to help you tune your guitar. This policy explains how the App handles your data.</p>

    <h2>Microphone Access</h2>
    <p>The App requires access to your device's microphone to detect the pitch of your instrument. Audio is processed <strong>locally on your
  device in real time</strong> and is never recorded, stored, or transmitted anywhere.</p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>The App does <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or share any personal data. No analytics, no tracking, no third-party SDKs.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The App does not use any third-party services.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>The App does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this page.</p>

